  "description": "A wide shot captures a vast, cracked and dry landscape, likely a desert or salt flat. The ground is covered in a network of polygon-shaped cracks, creating a textured, almost otherworldly surface. Sparse, low-lying shrubs dot the landscape, adding small points of green to the predominantly beige and brown color palette. In the distance, hazy mountain ranges rise, appearing muted and blue-gray under a bright blue sky with scattered white clouds. A lone individual, dressed in dark clothing, sits on the cracked earth, providing a sense of scale and solitude. The overall scene evokes a feeling of isolation and the harsh beauty of a desolate environment.",
